column1: **One sample out of 120 collected at the McMillan WTP in April was total coliform and E. coli positive. Additional analysis of the positive sample did not confirm the presence of E. coli in the sample. Investigation at the sample point indicated a high possibility that the sample may have been contaminated during sample
collection. All follow-up samples were negative for both total coliforms and E. coli .
